## Student Progress Tracking

### Physics-Specific Metrics
Track student understanding with physics-focused metrics:

```typescript
interface PhysicsProgress {
  conceptualMastery: {
    [concept: string]: {
      level: 'novice' | 'developing' | 'proficient' | 'advanced',
      lastAssessed: string,
      commonErrors: string[]
    }
  },
  problemSolvingSkills: {
    formulaSelection: number,    // 0-100 accuracy
    calculationAccuracy: number, // 0-100 accuracy  
    unitConsistency: number,     // 0-100 accuracy
    graphInterpretation: number  // 0-100 accuracy
  },
  unitProgress: {
    [unitId: string]: {
      lessonsCompleted: number,
      assignmentsCompleted: number,
      averageScore: number,
      timeSpent: number // minutes
    }
  }
}
```

